statements.sql: select * from `users` where `id` = 6 and `users`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1

select `users`.`id`, `users`.`name`, (SELECT count(*) FROM tarefas WHERE users.id = tarefas.user_id AND tarefas.data >= '1900-01-01' AND tarefas.data <= '2025-08-04') as tarefas_realizadas_count, (SELECT
COALESCE(
CONCAT(
FLOOR(AVG(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, tarefas.hora_inicio, tarefas.hora_fim)) / 3600),
'h ',
FLOOR((AVG(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, tarefas.hora_inicio, tarefas.hora_fim)) % 3600) / 60),
'm'
),
'0h 0m'
)
FROM tarefas
WHERE tarefas.user_id = users.id
AND tarefas.data >= '1900-01-01'
AND tarefas.data <= '2025-08-04'
) as media_tempo_formatado from `users` where exists (select 1 from `tarefas` where users.id = tarefas.user_id and `tarefas`.`data` >= '1900-01-01' and `tarefas`.`data` <= '2025-08-04') and `deleted_at` is null and `users`.`deleted_at` is null order by `id` asc, `tarefas_realizadas_count` desc
select count(*) as aggregate from `users` where `users`.`deleted_at` is null
